    "In other words, a one-way ANOVA test was done to ensure that the above improvement made by the students was because of the AI tool utilization but not any other variables or factors.",
    "Table 11 indicates a statically meaningful difference in writing test results between students with a dissimilar frequency of AI application with F (3, 56) = 14.941, p = 0.000 < 0.001.",
    "Therefore, it can be concluded that AI tools mainly contributed to the students' improvement in academic writing skills.",
    "That is to say, the more students apply AI tools, the higher the writing score they achieve.",
    "The findings of this study clearly show that AI-powered tools positively impact students' academic writing."
